</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Stroke Code Presentations, Interventions, and Outcomes Before and During the COVID-19 Pandemic</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Jasne%20AS"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Adam S Jasne</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Adam S Jasne</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Department of Neurology (A.S.J., P.C., I.M., R.M., M.E., Q.Z., K.N., K.V., M.A., N.P., G.J.F., P.L., N.Z., R.N., H.A., D.N., C.L., D.Y.H., J.S., S.S., K.N.S., L.H.S., R.S.), Yale University School of Medicine, New Haven, CT.</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Jasne%20AS"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Adam S Jasne</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chojecka%20P"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Pola Chojecka</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Pola Chojecka</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
